HEADWORD: Crow-trodden
<hw>Crow"-trod`den</hw> <pr>(kr⟦omac⟧"tr?d`d'n)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Marked with crow's-feet, or wrinkles, about the eyes.</def>
<mark>[Poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

